<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.617" end="00:00:22.200">En, to, En, to, tre, fire.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.278" end="00:00:23.520"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.582" end="00:00:25.691">Hvis du holder af James Brown musik,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.691" end="00:00:27.585">f&#229;r du en virkelig dejlig aften.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.585" end="00:00:29.761">I aften fejrer vi Black Velvet</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.761" end="00:00:33.850">James Brown, Jr.'s 62 &#229;rs f&#248;dselsdag.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.850" end="00:00:35.906" region="top"> Whoo, 62!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.476" end="00:00:38.526" region="top"> S&#229; nu vil jeg bede jeg give et stort bifald,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.526" end="00:00:39.758" region="top"> for vi har en ung mand</p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.758" end="00:00:41.545" region="top"> der kommer p&#229; scenen nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.545" end="00:00:43.690">Han har v&#230;ret med i David Letterman Show.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.690" end="00:00:45.777">Giv et bifald, m&#248;d og byd velkommen til</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.777" end="00:00:49.963">Black Velvet James Brown, Jr.!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.963" end="00:00:52.279"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.279" end="00:00:53.952"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.952" end="00:00:59.249">&#9834; Det en en mands verden. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.249" end="00:01:05.556">&#9834; Men jeg ville v&#230;re ingenting, ingenting ... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.556" end="00:01:06.715">- Jeg har spillet James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.715" end="00:01:13.956">siden jeg var 14 &#229;r gammel.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.956" end="00:01:16.475"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.475" end="00:01:17.935"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.935" end="00:01:21.271"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.271" end="00:01:25.860"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.860" end="00:01:29.767">Men nu vil jeg til at lave Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.767" end="00:01:52.445"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.599" end="00:01:54.471" region="top"> Mit f&#248;rste album med originale numre</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.471" end="00:01:58.132" region="top"> udkommer 25. januar.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.132" end="00:02:01.271">Jeg har k&#230;mpet i mere end 42 &#229;r</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.271" end="00:02:03.014">for at klare mig i denne industri</p>
      <p begin="00:02:03.014" end="00:02:04.731">og i en alder af 62 &#229;r,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.731" end="00:02:06.775">er jeg ved at finde den rette vej.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09.086" end="00:02:11.071">Jeg har aldrig tjent nok</p>
      <p begin="00:02:11.071" end="00:02:13.928">p&#229; musikken til at kunne leve af det.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.928" end="00:02:15.993">Men jeg h&#229;ber at dette album</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.993" end="00:02:17.442">vil blive et vendepunkt for mig,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.442" end="00:02:20.252">at jeg kan leve af musik nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.314" end="00:02:26.837">Hey, mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.837" end="00:02:28.808">Jeg finder lidt vand til dig, OK?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.808" end="00:02:30.155">Hey, mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.155" end="00:02:30.834">Det er min fugl.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.834" end="00:02:32.647">G&#248;r mig vred.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.647" end="00:02:33.782">Jeg bliver vred, jeg g&#229;r v&#230;k fra det,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.782" end="00:02:35.520">g&#229;r ind i det rum, lukker d&#248;ren,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.520" end="00:02:37.328">og lader ham r&#229;be det han vil.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.020" end="00:02:39.057">Og jag har mit eget lille sted,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:39.057" end="00:02:40.590">det er ikke det jeg &#248;nsker,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.590" end="00:02:43.199">men Gud ske tak, har jeg tak over hovedet.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.221" end="00:02:45.529">N&#229;r jeg g&#229;r ind i min lille lejlighed</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.529" end="00:02:47.113">og l&#229;ser min d&#248;r,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:47.113" end="00:02:48.734">s&#229; har jeg fred.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.734" end="00:02:50.496">N&#229;r n&#229;r jeg g&#229;r ned til ghettoen,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.496" end="00:02:53.225">g&#229;r ind i elevatoren,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.225" end="00:02:54.807">n&#229;r man kommer ind i den,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.407" end="00:02:55.545">det er der problemerne begynder.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.545" end="00:02:57.076">Du ved aldrig</p>
      <p begin="00:02:57.076" end="00:02:59.174">hvad der sker i disse ting.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:59.174" end="00:03:00.663">Fyren nedenfor,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.663" end="00:03:02.366">hans navn er Alfred,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.366" end="00:03:03.206">en rigtig god fyr, gjorde ingen fortr&#230;d.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.206" end="00:03:04.783">En kirkens mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.783" end="00:03:06.731">De sk&#248;d l&#248;s p&#229; hans sted.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.731" end="00:03:07.753">Han viste mig alle hullerne</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.753" end="00:03:08.478">hvor de sk&#248;d op i stedet.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.478" end="00:03:09.261">Jeg sagde, wow, mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.261" end="00:03:10.741">Jeg sagde,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.741" end="00:03:13.017">"&#216;h, jeg kunne ikke leve p&#229; f&#248;rste sal."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13.017" end="00:03:14.586">N&#229;r det bliver for</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.586" end="00:03:16.289">vildt i ghettoen,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.289" end="00:03:18.007">tager jeg til min mors hus</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.007" end="00:03:19.737">og jeg sover i hendes k&#230;lder.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32.075" end="00:03:33.691">S&#229; jeg kommer her</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.691" end="00:03:36.011">og det er hvor jeg overnatter.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:36.011" end="00:03:37.269">Indtil n&#230;ste dag,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.269" end="00:03:39.058">jeg tager mig af deres &#230;rinder,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.058" end="00:03:40.105">s&#248;rger for det hele</p>
      <p begin="00:03:40.105" end="00:03:43.638">for at vi kan have tag over hovederne.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.931" end="00:03:47.370">Jeg tager gerne lidt af dette</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.370" end="00:03:48.964">i en lille kugle.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.953" end="00:03:53.302">Kom ogs&#229; disse i.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.722" end="00:03:56.898">Hey, hvordan er risen?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:57.067" end="00:03:58.366">- Lad mig se?</p>
      <p begin="00:04:00.135" end="00:04:02.056">Bare lidt mere.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:02.194" end="00:04:05.126">- Jeg kom fra en familie p&#229; otte.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:05.188" end="00:04:08.021">Hovedsagen er at passe p&#229;</p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.021" end="00:04:11.799">min mor og g&#248;re hvad jeg kan.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.707" end="00:04:14.664" region="top"> - Det er min lille dreng,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.664" end="00:04:16.777" region="top"> og jeg elsker ham.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.883" end="00:04:18.556" region="top"> Han vasker mit t&#248;j.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.726" end="00:04:19.466" region="top"> Han g&#248;r huset rent.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.466" end="00:04:20.945" region="top"> P&#229; Valentins dag,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.945" end="00:04:23.555" region="top"> gav han mig en &#230;ske slik.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.555" end="00:04:24.911" region="top"> Min lille baby er</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.911" end="00:04:26.138" region="top"> lige s&#229; s&#248;d som det slik.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:26.138" end="00:04:27.835">- Jeg pr&#248;ver bare at give</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.835" end="00:04:28.542">hende et fredfyldt liv,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.542" end="00:04:29.668">og</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.668" end="00:04:31.712">s&#229; hun ikke skal bekymre sig om</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.712" end="00:04:33.312">regninger og den slags.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.312" end="00:04:34.478">Jeg tog det p&#229; mine skuldre</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.478" end="00:04:36.190">og jeg virkelig,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:36.190" end="00:04:37.831">jeg vidste nok ikke hvad det var jeg kastede mig ud i.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.831" end="00:04:38.493">Men nu er jeg i det.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.493" end="00:04:40.083">Det vil jeg ikke &#230;ndre.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.083" end="00:04:41.252">S&#229; det eneste jeg kan pr&#248;ve at</p>
      <p begin="00:04:41.252" end="00:04:42.968">g&#248;re er at f&#229; noget til at lykkes,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.968" end="00:04:44.297">hvor jeg kan tjene en rimelig indkomst,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.297" end="00:04:47.211">s&#229; jeg kan leve og lade leve.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:47.211" end="00:04:50.030">Og det er det eneste jeg &#248;nsker i livet nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:50.138" end="00:04:56.875"/>
      <p begin="00:04:56.875" end="00:05:00.615">&#9834; Vi k&#248;rer rundt og rundt igen.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.615" end="00:05:05.222">&#9834;Hvor det stopper, ved ingen. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:05.222" end="00:05:08.565">&#9834; Det er en kold, kold verden &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.965" end="00:05:12.469">&#9834; Det er en kold, kold verden. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:14.254" end="00:05:16.173">&#9834; Hvordan kan vi stopper forandringerne, &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:16.173" end="00:05:21.219">&#9834; der sker i Amerika i dag? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:31.033" end="00:05:35.022">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.466" end="00:05:43.575">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.575" end="00:05:47.287">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage til den Gyldne Regel. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:47.287" end="00:05:48.994">&#9834; Oh. Ah. Uh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.455" end="00:05:50.963">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.963" end="00:05:55.504">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage til den Gyldne Regel. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.504" end="00:05:58.215">&#9834; D&#230;mp det lidt &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.215" end="00:06:11.844"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.844" end="00:06:13.438">- Det er en sang</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.438" end="00:06:15.399">fra den nye plade, "No Time For Dreaming".</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.399" end="00:06:16.525">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.525" end="00:06:17.652">og the Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.652" end="00:06:19.111">Jeg kan ikke tro</p>
      <p begin="00:06:19.111" end="00:06:20.445">at du kom ud af intet</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.445" end="00:06:22.656">som n&#230;sten ukendt for os.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.656" end="00:06:24.858">Har du indspillet f&#248;r?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.981" end="00:06:26.277">- Nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:26.277" end="00:06:28.820">Det er f&#248;rste jeg jeg udkommer.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.820" end="00:06:30.349">- Jeg ved du har optr&#229;dt.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:30.349" end="00:06:31.431">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.931" end="00:06:32.920">- Som Black Velvet.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.920" end="00:06:34.044">-Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.044" end="00:06:35.335">- S&#229; nu optr&#230;der du som-</p>
      <p begin="00:06:35.335" end="00:06:37.064">som Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.064" end="00:06:38.076">- Jah, jah.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.076" end="00:06:39.298">- Jamen, du har bestemt et fantastisk band</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.298" end="00:06:40.129">bag dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:40.129" end="00:06:41.667">Og selvf&#248;lgelig</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.667" end="00:06:43.302">med folkene over p&#229; Daptone,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:43.302" end="00:06:44.463">du ved,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.463" end="00:06:45.287">det er et storartet hold.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:45.287" end="00:06:46.597">Og du har set</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.597" end="00:06:49.276">hvad der skete med Sharon Jones, som, - Ja, ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49.276" end="00:06:51.340">du ved, like som du,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:51.340" end="00:06:52.882">gik fra komplet ukendt til</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.897" end="00:06:55.464">hvem ved hvilke h&#248;jder du kan n&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.464" end="00:06:56.872">S&#229; det,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.872" end="00:06:59.067">det m&#229; v&#230;re et sp&#230;ndende &#248;jeblik for dig?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:59.067" end="00:07:01.820">- Jeg tror Gud lige har svarret p&#229; mine b&#248;nner,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.820" end="00:07:03.864">du ved, det bare ligesom.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.864" end="00:07:06.033">Jeg spurgte mig selv, hvorfor det tog s&#229; lang tid,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:06.033" end="00:07:07.451">men du kan ikke stille sp&#248;rgsm&#229;lstegn ved Gud</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.451" end="00:07:09.411">n&#229;r han vil g&#248;re ting.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:09.411" end="00:07:12.348">S&#229; i min h&#248;je alder begyndte det bare at komme.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:12.348" end="00:07:13.916">- Hvad er det n&#230;ste?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.916" end="00:07:15.375">Jeg mener, t&#230;nker du stort?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15.375" end="00:07:17.144">- Jeg mener at der er ingen gr&#230;nser.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:17.144" end="00:07:19.421">- Tillykke med denne fantastiske plade.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:19.421" end="00:07:20.737">Uanset hvad der sker med den,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.737" end="00:07:22.632">er det et fint stykke kunst.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.632" end="00:07:24.943">Charles Bradley p&#229; WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:25.113" end="00:07:28.346"/>
      <p begin="00:07:28.346" end="00:07:33.685">&#9834; Denne verden g&#229;r i flammer. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.685" end="00:07:39.107">&#9834; Og ingen vil tage skylden. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:39.107" end="00:07:44.286">&#9834; Fort&#230;l mig ikke, hvordan jeg skal leve mit liv. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:44.286" end="00:07:49.746">&#9834; N&#229;r du aldrig har f&#248;lt smerten. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.746" end="00:07:55.790">&#9834; Ohhh. Ahhh. Ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.790" end="00:07:58.335">&#9834;Ohhh.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:58.335" end="00:08:01.051">&#9834; Kan de ikke se jeg gr&#230;der? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:01.051" end="00:08:02.883" region="top"> &#9834; Ohhh... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.883" end="00:08:04.800"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.800" end="00:08:06.051" region="top"> - Jeg ved ikke hvor mange kunstnere</p>
      <p begin="00:08:06.051" end="00:08:07.718" region="top"> der har v&#230;ret over 62 &#229;r gamle</p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.718" end="00:08:09.445" region="top"> og udgivet deres debut plade.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.213" end="00:08:11.950" region="top"> Han er m&#229;ske den f&#248;rste.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.777" end="00:08:14.936" region="top"> - Denne fyr har fattet det,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.936" end="00:08:16.937" region="top"> f&#229;r gang i den, efter min mening.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.937" end="00:08:19.215" region="top"> - Han har arbejdet meget h&#229;rdt i lang tid.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:19.338" end="00:08:20.858" region="top"> Og jeg h&#229;ber at-</p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.858" end="00:08:21.734" region="top"> nok folk kan h&#248;re ham synge,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.734" end="00:08:23.151">s&#229; at-</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.151" end="00:08:24.361">han kan skabe sig det liv han &#248;nsker sig,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24.361" end="00:08:26.139">og tage sig af sin familie.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:26.139" end="00:08:27.626"/>
      <p begin="00:08:27.626" end="00:08:30.701">&#9834; Uh. Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.701" end="00:08:33.120">&#9834; Jeg taler til dig t&#248;s &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:33.120" end="00:08:34.538">&#9834; Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.538" end="00:08:36.642">&#9834; Kun du ... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.642" end="00:08:38.333">Jeg gik til Gabe</p>
      <p begin="00:08:38.333" end="00:08:40.502">fordi jeg mente at han ved hvad han g&#248;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:40.502" end="00:08:42.129">Og jeg f&#248;lte at han kunne give mig en hj&#230;lpende h&#229;nd</p>
      <p begin="00:08:42.129" end="00:08:44.673">hvor jeg kan komme ind i musik branchen.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:44.673" end="00:08:48.569">Det eneste jeg vidste var hvordan jeg kom op p&#229; en scene og optr&#230;de.</p>
